Class StudentList

  • java.lang.Object
    • StudentList

  • public class StudentList
extends java.lang.Object
    Container class to hold students registered for school, holds Student and its subclasses Uses an array to hold the objects.
    Author:
    Rizwan Chowdhury, Tin Fung
